From: Yuval Mintz <yuvalmin@broadcom.com>
Date: Wed, 9 Jan 2013 14:39:33 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 08/27] bnx2x: Clean previous IGU status before ack
git-commit: ebe61d80b42662a1cf8d24e0b8605aa16fa6e4d0
References: FATE#313915 bnc#790597
Patch-mainline: v3.9-rc1

When enabling interrupts, acknowledge the interrupt only
after configuring the IGU to the correct interrupt mode
(otherwise it would dirty selftests)

Signed-off-by: Yuval Mintz <yuvalmin@broadcom.com>
Signed-off-by: Ariel Elior <ariele@broadcom.com>
Signed-off-by: Eilon Greenstein <eilong@broadcom.com>
Acked-by: Lee Duncan <lduncan@suse.com>
